<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TMaL32">
<l>ārttuvaṇ ṭalampuñ cōlai yaṇitiru varaṅkan taṉṉuḷ</l>
<l>kārttira ḷaṉaiya mēṉik kaṇṇaṉē yuṉṉaik kāṇum</l>
<l>mārkkamoṉ ṟaṟiya māṭṭā maṉicariṟ turica ṉāya</l>
<l>mūrkkaṉēṉ vantu niṉṟēṉ mūrkkaṉēṉ mūrkka ṉēṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O Kaṇṇaṉ whose body is akin to a cluster of clouds [who dwells]</l>
<l>inside Śrīraṅgam adorned with groves where bees wander about buzzing loudly!</l>
<l>I, an ignorant person, who am the [most] wicked among men</l>
<l rend="indent">who do not know any way of seeing You</l>
<l>have come [and] stood [here],</l>
<l>I, an ignorant person, I, an ignorant person!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
